    <string name="guide_trading_title">Trading Cards for Coins</string>
    <string name="guide_trading_desc">If you have extra utility cards, you can trade them for coins in the shop! Just tap on the card in your inventory and select \'Trade\'.</string>
    
    <string name="guide_faq">Frequently Asked Questions</string>
    
    <string name="guide_faq_1_q">How do I change the language?</string>
    <string name="guide_faq_1_a">You can change the language by going to Settings and selecting your preferred language from the list.</string>
    
    <string name="guide_faq_2_q">What happens if I run out of time?</string>
    <string name="guide_faq_2_a">If you run out of time before answering a question, it will be marked as incorrect and you\'ll move to the next question.</string>
    
    <string name="guide_faq_3_q">Can I play without internet?</string>
    <string name="guide_faq_3_a">Yes! Some quizzes are available offline. Look for the offline symbol next to the quiz category.</string>
    
    <string name="guide_faq_4_q">How do I earn trophies?</string>
    <string name="guide_faq_4_a">Trophies are earned by completing quizzes with high scores. The more questions you answer correctly, the better trophy you\'ll receive!</string>
    
    <string name="guide_faq_5_q">Can I create my own quizzes?</string>
    <string name="guide_faq_5_a">Not yet, but we\'re working on adding this feature in a future update!</string>
    
